Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've woken me up some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to discuss something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the sort of attitude you should have when you're asking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that you'll benefit from anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so skeptical?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I do, I want you to come to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, you're from the class next to ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't hear you! Can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Elen's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fujieda Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the same class during freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you want something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... I just wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something about Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to ask about is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anyone you like right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it wouldn't be someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who you were talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly wanted to eat Kanekoya's waffles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to ask Mio if she'd tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I intrude on something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barged right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was confessing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Fujiwara-san was about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's taste is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did you reply to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barged in before I could, then-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Mio would really want to hear a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might sound weird coming from the one who barged in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you can't just ignore her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I went all the way to set it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just get to the main points?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just followed the game plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I like you, so be my boyfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just strangle him until he agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take longer than five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confessing is a blitzkrieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final spring of your school life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on wasting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to look for you after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I found you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to say to Fujieda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the hell out of your sight right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda-san, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just too sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit peeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did you reply to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's just start off by being friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such an ordinary reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no taste in it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you make any plans with that friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going into town tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to embarrass her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supporting you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I could tell right after our small chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some temporary pocket money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already gave you this month's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're already going on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great step forward for our late blooming Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you girls talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie, this is a major event!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Mio's going on-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring your boxed lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now it's 40 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Review what I told you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of host are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tasted really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to take you to a restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live alone with Elen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our parents died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel anything special about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live alone with my mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But knowing that my mother works so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes wish I had a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to support your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need a guy for anything, I'm always around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like Sanae's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to a place that you can't say...{protip: love hotel}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san, what sort of a place is "a place that you can't say"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After boarding the staircase that leads to adulthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll become Cinderella! {wat}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you complete the schedule I gave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your date will end perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that she's riding such a big motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never be able to buy such an awesome bike since I'm destined to be poor-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When did...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the sound was hidden by a silencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a 9mm parabellum bullet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woke me up from my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling from Mexico to Peru by land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from the Palau Islands to the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it's been half a year since we've settled in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've forgotten our past and continued to live on here... On this piece of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed a lot after coming to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is opening up slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a hometown is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I received a silent warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's time we wake up from our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were possible, I'd like you to keep staying in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To forget what you've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still need a confession of my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession of your sins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To God directly, because I'll meet with Him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno is finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make use Fujieda-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda-san's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Elen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after giving birth to her, Fujieda-san's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard about it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around her told her that her father had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, she still believes that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father is important enough to be in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godoh Kaiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the large-area mafia group - the Godoh Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godoh Group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda is a surname from her mother's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Godoh Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even inside the Godoh Group, only a few know of Mio's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire reason was to protect his separated wife and daughter from the power struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Mio and Godoh Daisuke are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, siblings through the same father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godoh Kaiten doesn't want his daughter involved in any mayhem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he can't protect her out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio is Godoh Kaiten's biggest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was from a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I told you that after Master escaped from Inferno,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was hiding in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Master thoroughly investigated the Godoh Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master also planned on using this weakness if he had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to use Fujieda-san to threaten the Godoh Group?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, it can be our ace card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:15:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the young leader holding the Godoh Group's power is Shiga Toru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you understand the situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's Inferno you're going against, as long as you hold Mio as a hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I should've told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had known that Mio was interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had known that they'd be here so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our life here was surprisingly short.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make preparations to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you can still be like how you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be too selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to be prepared for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've already forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past six months, your smile and sleeping face were filled with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at you like that made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the hometown you were born in can bring peace to your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the dream I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you promised me that one day you'd bring me back to my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the happiness you had up until now to be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can come back another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we leave, this country won't just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely be able to come back to your hometown some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A day will come when we can live truly normal lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that day is not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji left in the middle of the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Reiji-san said he had something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For young people in their prime,\Nnothing is more important than love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even gave him a schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should just mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, "I guess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji-san, I had a lot of fun yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take care of your important matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good to be able to block my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a little worse than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business with Elen, so I need to go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going\Nand leaving your girlfriend behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels different...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, putting that aside... Is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ghosts that cannot exist anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are phantoms with no identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I call you... the Old Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
